init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf came to the 92nd little pig's house and said, "Little pig, little pig, let me come in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Pig said, "Well, I'm not going to let you in, so you'll just have to go hungry."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He went to the store and bought a bunch of dynamite.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the Pig was like, "Dude, that's not going to work.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My house is made out of depleted uranium."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the wolf was like, "Oh, I guess I'll have to try something else."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He went to the store and bought a bunch of grenades.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Pig said, "Well, I'm sorry, but I'm not going to let you in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, I'm going to go to the store and get some food.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Pig said, "No thanks, I'm not hungry."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Pig said, "I'm sorry, but I'm not going to let you in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then the wolf said, "I'm still hungry."
